				<text>7.3.1.2 Task: compute these 2x2 determinants</text>
		</name>
    <questiontext format="moodle_auto_format">
				<text><![CDATA[<p class="HELM_exercise">Exercise</p>
<p>Evaluate the determinants of the following matrices.</p>
<ol class="HELM_parts_inline">
<li>\(A={@matrixa@}\)</li>
<li>\(B={@matrixb@}\)</li>
<li>\(C={@matrixc@}\)</li></ol>

<ol class="HELM_parts">

<li><p>\(\det{A}=\) [[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]] [[feedback:prt1]]</p></li>

<li><p>\(\det{B}=\) [[input:ans2]] [[validation:ans2]] [[feedback:prt2]]</p></li>

<li><p>\(\det{C}=\) [[input:ans3]] [[validation:ans3]] [[feedback:prt3]]</p></li>

</ol>]]></text>
		</questiontext>
    <generalfeedback format="moodle_auto_format">
				<text><![CDATA[<p>We use the definition to find the determinant of the following matrices.</p>
<ol class="HELM_parts">
  <li><p>For \(A={@matrixa@},\)</p>
    <p>\(\det(A) = {@detAA@} = {@ta1@}.\)</p>
    </li>
    <li><p>For \(B={@matrixb@},\)</p>
      <p>\(\det(B) = {@detBB@} = {@ta2@}.\)</p>
    </li>
    <li><p>For \(C={@matrixc@},\)</p>
      <p>\(\det(C) = {@detCC@} = {@ta3@}.\)</p>
  </li>
</ol>]]></text>
		</generalfeedback>
